sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as User
    participant W as Web/Mobile App
    participant G as API Gateway
    participant I as Identity Service
    participant GO as Google Identity

    alt Email + password
        U->>W: Enter email + password
        W->>G: POST /auth/login
        G->>I: Verify credentials
        I->>I: Check hash, check lockout
        I-->>G: Session token (or "incorrect")
        G-->>W: Logged in / rejected
    else Sign in with Google
        U->>W: Tap "Sign in with Google"
        W->>GO: Google sign-in
        GO-->>W: Google identity proof
        W->>G: POST /auth/google
        G->>I: Verify proof with Google
        I->>GO: Validate token
        GO-->>I: Valid + Google subject id
        I->>I: Find or create account
        I-->>G: Session token
        G-->>W: Logged in
    end
